      "ticketPrice": "Free (some attractions charge)",
      "recommendedVisitTime": "2-3 hours",
      "highlights": [
        "Canal boat rides",
        "Night lighting",
        "Traditional snacks",
        "Ancient bridges"
      ],
      "tips": "Best at night when illuminated. Take a boat ride. Try local snacks. Less crowded than Pingjiang Road."
    },
    {
